fields.name: Description
fields.description: Description of the newly generated repository.

fields.name: IsPrivate
fields.description: Whether or not the newly generated repository is a private repository. Defaults to false (i.e. public).

fields.name: Owner
fields.description: Owner of the newly generated repository.

fields.name: RepositoryName
fields.description: Name of the newly generated repository.

fields.name: TemplateRepositoryUrl
fields.description: URL of the template repository. The newly generated repository will be based on this one.
